[[SECTION]]
TITLE: 2. Scope and Boundary

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-SPPB-ROOT
TITLE: GHOST SuperPrompt Projection and Prompt Builder Scope
STATEMENT: >>>
This file is a draft child requirement file in the GHOST StrictDoc requirement tree.

It owns current SuperPrompt projection and Prompt Builder behavior.

It shall not redefine prompt preprocessing, Knowledge Management, Memory Management, GUI layout, or final LLM answer generation.

This file shall not duplicate detailed requirements owned by sibling files.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-CIPA-ROOT

